  "texts": [
    "In LM literature, Swayamdipta et al. (2020) have categorized data into three difficulty levels for non-generative tasks through 'data map' approach.",
    "Later, numerous works such as",
    "Li et al. (2024); Lu et al.",
    "(2024); Chen et al. (2024b); Liu et al.",
    "(2024); Kung et al. (2023) have been proposed with the aim to increase instruction tuning efficiency."
  ]
}